  <link rel="canonical" href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/terms/">
  <meta name="description" content="Terms of use for stackarchitect.xyz — conditions governing use of the site, free tools, guides, and the Complete Kit. Last updated April 2026.">
  <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
  <meta name="author" content="Stack Architect">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website"><meta property="og:url" content="https://stackarchitect.xyz/terms/"><meta property="og:title" content="Terms of Use — Stack Architect"><meta property="og:description" content="Terms of use for stackarchitect.xyz."><meta property="og:site_name" content="Stack Architect">
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en-GB" href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/terms/"><link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/terms/"><link rel="alternate" hreflang="x-default" href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/terms/">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"><link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link rel="preload" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700;800&display=swap" as="style" onload="this.onload=null;this.rel=\'stylesheet\'" />
  <noscript><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700;800&display=swap" /></noscript>
  <style>
    *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
    :root{--sans:'Inter',-apple-system,sans-serif;--mono:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;--bg:#0a0a0a;--bg-2:#111;--text:#f0efe8;--text-2:#c8c7c0;--text-3:#888780;--text-4:#555450;--g:#00c864;--border:rgba(255,255,255,0.08)}
    body{font-family:var(--sans);background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);line-height:1.7}
    a{color:var(--g);text-decoration:none}a:hover{text-decoration:underline}
    .nav{background:var(--bg-2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:0 24px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100}
    .nav-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;height:52px;flex-wrap:wrap}
    .dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--g);display:inline-block}
    .nav-status{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text-4);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
    .nav-links{list-style:none;display:flex;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap;flex:1}
    .nl{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--text-3);text-decoration:none;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:4px}.nl:hover{color:var(--text);text-decoration:none}.nl-home{color:var(--g)}
    .nav-cta{margin-left:auto;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
    .ticker{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--g);letter-spacing:.1em}
    .btn-nav{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#000;background:var(--g);padding:8px 14px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap}
    .bc{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:14px 24px 0;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--text-4);display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center}
    .bc a{color:var(--text-4);text-decoration:none}.bc-sep{opacity:.4}
    .hero{padding:60px 24px 48px;text-align:center}.hero-inner{max-width:680px;margin:0 auto}
    .tag{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--g);background:rgba(0,200,100,.08);border:1px solid rgba(0,200,100,.2);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:20px}
    h1{font-size:clamp(28px,5vw,40px);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-.03em;line-height:1.1;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:14px}
    .dateline{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--text-4)}
    .prose-wrap{padding:0 24px 80px}.prose-inner{max-width:680px;margin:0 auto}
    .prose h2{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin:40px 0 12px}.prose h2:first-child{margin-top:0}
    .prose p{font-size:15px;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px}
    .prose ul{padding-left:20px;margin-bottom:16px}.prose li{font-size:15px;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:6px}
    footer{background:var(--bg-2);border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:48px 24px 32px;margin-top:40px}.ft{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
    .ft-strip{background:rgba(0,200,100,.06);border:1px solid rgba(0,200,100,.15);border-radius:10px;padding:20px 24px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:40px}
    .ft-strip-txt{font-size:14px;color:var(--text-2)}.ft-strip-txt span{font-weight:700;color:var(--text)}
    .ft-strip-cta{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#000;background:var(--g);padding:10px 18px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap}
    .ft-title{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-4);letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;display:block;margin-bottom:16px}
    .ft-links,.ft-sec{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px;margin-bottom:12px}
    .ft-links a,.ft-sec a{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--text-4);text-decoration:none;padding:3px 8px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px}
    .ft-trust{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;margin-bottom:24px}
    .tb{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text-4);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
    .tb-dot{width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--g);display:inline-block}
    .ft-div{border:none;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin:24px 0}
    .ft-ret{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text-4);text-decoration:none;display:block;margin-bottom:16px}
    .ft-copy{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text-4);margin-bottom:12px}
    .ft-disc{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-4);line-height:1.6}.ft-disc a{color:var(--text-4)}
    .sb{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text-4);margin-bottom:24px}
    .sb-sep{width:1px;height:12px;background:var(--border)}
  </style>
  <!-- GA4 -->
  <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-TE6Z6CW514"></script>
  <script>
    window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
    function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
    gtag('js', new Date());
    gtag('config', 'G-TE6Z6CW514');
  </script>

    <!-- Feed discovery -->
    <link rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" title="Stack Architect — Shopify Automation Guides" href="/rss.xml" />
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "WebSite", "@id": "https://stackarchitect.xyz/#website", "url": "https://stackarchitect.xyz/", "name": "Stack Architect", "description": "Free Shopify automation tools replacing $700+/month of paid apps \u2014 server-side tracking, inventory, email, TikTok Events API, P&L.", "publisher": {"@id": "https://stackarchitect.xyz/#org"}, "inLanguage": "en-GB"})} />
  </head>
<body>
<Nav />
<div class="bc"><a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/">Home</a><span class="bc-sep">/</span><span style="color:var(--text-3)">Terms of Use</span></div>
<main id="main-content">
  <div class="hero"><div class="hero-inner"><div class="tag">Legal</div><h1>Terms of Use</h1><p class="dateline">Last updated: April 2026</p></div></div>
  <div class="prose-wrap"><div class="prose-inner"><div class="prose">
    <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
    <p>By accessing or using stackarchitect.xyz, you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, do not use the site.</p>
    <h2>Use of Free Tools and Guides</h2>
    <p>The free tools, guides, and downloadable resources on this site are provided for use by Shopify store owners on their own stores. You may not resell, redistribute, or repackage Stack Architect tools or guides as your own products or services without written permission.</p>
    <h2>The Complete Kit — Paid Product</h2>
    <p>The Complete Kit ($29 one-time) is a digital product delivered via Stripe. Due to its digital nature, all sales are final. If files are not delivered or are materially defective, contact us via the support link and we will resolve the issue. The Kit is licensed for use on your own Shopify store(s) — not for resale or redistribution.</p>
    <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
    <p>This site contains affiliate links to third-party services. We may earn a commission if you sign up via these links at no extra cost to you. All affiliate relationships are disclosed on the relevant pages. We are not responsible for the performance, pricing changes, or terms of third-party services.</p>
    <h2>No Warranty</h2>
    <p>All tools, guides, and content are provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. Stack Architect does not guarantee that the tools will achieve any specific outcome for your store. Results described on the site are based on typical store experiences and may vary.</p>
    <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, Stack Architect is not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the site, tools, or guides — including loss of revenue, loss of data, or disruption to your store's operations.</p>
    <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p>All content on this site is the intellectual property of Stack Architect. You may share links to pages on this site. You may not reproduce substantial portions of content without attribution and a link back to the original page.</p>
    <h2>Governing Law</h2>
    <p>These terms are governed by the laws of England and Wales.</p>
    <h2>Changes to These Terms</h2>
    <p>We may update these terms from time to time. The "last updated" date at the top reflects the most recent revision. Continued use of the site constitutes acceptance of any updated terms.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For questions about these terms, use the support link in the footer navigation.</p>
  </div></div></div>
</main>
<Footer />
<script>document.getElementById('ft-copy').textContent='© '+new Date().getFullYear()+' STACK_ARCHITECT // CORE_DEPLOYMENT';</script>
</body>
</html>
